行核酸检测，确保您能做到“三天一检、放心出行”。 来源：北京日报"},"attached_info":"Cj4IhoqygfbM16AmEAMaCDgyNTY4OTIwIKyahZYGMAM4SkAecgk1NDEyOTE2NDN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"81 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"31_1656915404.606894","card_id":"Q_466319507","target":{"id":466319507,"title":"开车与不开车的人思维上有差距吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/466319507","type":"question","created":1624256113,"answer_count":437,"follower_count":1221,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[570,9944,15926,19156],"comment_count":13,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8IhoqygfbM16AmEAMaCDY1OTA2MTg2IPHcwIYGMA04xQlAH3IJNDY2MzE5NTA3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"80 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-cc0e95411c1b412df15d4e8fd2941254_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"32_1656915404.6073868","card_id":"Q_541377329","target":{"id":541377329,"title":"《原神》 2.8 - 3.2该怎么规划抽卡？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/541377329","type":"question","created":1656892829,"answer_count":32,"follower_count":36,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[187376,406546],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"2.8万叶可莉宵宫 3.0驴哥钟离甘雨 3.1妮露赛诺 3.2草神散兵 现有原石储备最多只能10选4，该如何取舍？"},"attached_info":"Cj4IhoqygfbM16AmEAMaCDgyNTg3OTYxIJ3biJYGMAA4JEAgcgk1NDEzNzczMjl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"74 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"33_1656915404.6079261","card_id":"Q_541191844","target":{"id":541191844,"title":"第 33 届金曲奖蔡健雅获最佳女歌手，为什么蔡健雅可以四封金曲歌后？",